10:24.920 --> 10:29.198
You bet we do. This is Big Ben's.
We got canteens 365 days a year.

10:29.360 --> 10:32.591
- Which one of these can I fix you up with?
- This blue one.

10:32.760 --> 10:37.038
- Hey, sport, where did you run off to?
- This man was helping me find my canteen.

10:37.200 --> 10:42.399
