12:05.600 --> 12:08.672
<i>Today's my birthday.
Look what they gave me.</i>

12:08.840 --> 12:10.159
Junior!

12:10.320 --> 12:14.438
Junior! What is taking you so long?

12:14.600 --> 12:18.752
